  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Insulin Detemir in Type 2 Diabetes Inadequately Controlled on OHA Therapy Alone</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Efficacy and the Safety of Insulin Detemir and Insulin NPH as add-on to Current OHA Therapy in Subjects With type2 Diabetes Mellitus</official_title>
