  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Japan. The aim of this trial is to investigate the efficacy of
      insulin detemir on blood glucose control in type 2 diabetes when added to current OHA
      treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
